<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>Participation is a unique focus of the <span class="title-main">Theatre &amp; Dance </span>minor, encouraging students to become familiar with the myriad roles involved in planning, producing, and bringing performances to the stage. Techniques of acting, directing, stagecraft, or dance develop skills in communication, creativity, and collaboration.</p>
]]>
</quickviewtext>
